h cabbage slaw and avocado\"\n  },\n  \"Saturday\": {\n    \"Breakfast\": \"Greek yogurt pancakes topped with fresh berries\",\n    \"Lunch\": \"Grilled vegetable and hummus wrap\",\n    \"Dinner\": \"Lean beef stir-fry with broccoli, carrots, and brown rice\"\n  },\n  \"Sunday\": {\n    \"Breakfast\": \"Smoothie bowl with mixed berries, granola, and pumpkin seeds\",\n    \"Lunch\": \"Grilled chicken Caesar salad with light dressing\",\n    \"Dinner\": \"Baked cod with roasted Brussels sprouts and sweet potato mash\"\n  }\n}"},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.outputParserStructured","typeVersion":1.3,"position":[1040,480],"id":"4dc1dc7f-e59d-42b9-9dab-1f8e78ce839b","name":"Structured Output Parser2"},{"parameters":{},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.memoryBufferWindow","typeVersion":1.3,"position":[128,224],"id":"2cd78309-bdb6-4bec-992d-e605a5fb8bb1","name":"Simple Memory"},{"parameters":{},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.memoryBufferWindow","typeVersion":1.3,"position":[960,880],"id":"18c9090e-2467-4e9b-a38b-aa06f7d8466d","name":"Simple Memory4"},{"parameters":{},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.memoryBufferWindow","typeVersion":1.3,"position":[912,528],"id":"c1d878b7-1336-4b7e-9a83-a1cd4d5bd625","name":"Simple Memory3"},{"parameters":{},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.memoryBufferWindow","typeVersion":1.3,"position":[912,176],"id":"9de375b5-8013-4b9b-9f95-71d66db90257","name":"Simple Memory2"},{"parameters":{},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.memoryBufferWindow","typeVersion":1.3,"position":[912,-176],"id":"7d819874-2b89-42e4-ab0c-2242c2fa1109","name":"Simple Memory1"}],"connections":{"When chat message received":{"main":[[{"node":"Message Type agent","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Structured Output Parser":{"ai_outputParser":[[{"node":"Message Type agent","type":"ai_outputParser","index":0}]]},"Google Gemini Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Message Type agent","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Message Type agent":{"main":[[{"node":"Switch","type"